  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/663530/extras/7e711d7e3c8ad77d9941be80088a4399.avif?t=1572447164\" width=512 height=144 /></span><br><br>It started out as just your usual Saturday morning game of golf.<br>But what's this?<br>The ball went into the hole on the first green and when you went to investigate, you fell into the deepest rabbit hole ever (like, super deep) and ended up in a suit of armor in a dungeon!<br>The distant sound of dragon-burp wafts up from the depths.<br>Well, may as well go search for your ball!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Real Time Roguelike Action.<br></li><li>New random Generated Dungeons Each Game.<br></li><li>Game editor For Making Your Own custom Maps.<br></li><li>Play the 12 level fiendishly difficult \"Underpar\" custom map (included).<br></li><li>Permanent death - once you're dead - you're dead.<br></li><li>Steam integrated with stats and achievements.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/663530/extras/7e711d7e3c8ad77d9941be80088a4399.avif?t=1572447164\" width=512 height=144 /></span><br><br>It started out as just your usual Saturday morning game of golf.<br>But what's this?<br>The ball went into the hole on the first green and when you went to investigate, you fell into the deepest rabbit hole ever (like, super deep) and ended up in a suit of armor in a dungeon!<br>The distant sound of dragon-burp wafts up from the depths.<br>Well, may as well go search for your ball!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Real Time Roguelike Action.<br></li><li>New random Generated Dungeons Each Game.<br></li><li>Game editor For Making Your Own custom Maps.<br></li><li>Play the 12 level fiendishly difficult \"Underpar\" custom map (included).<br></li><li>Permanent death - once you're dead - you're dead.<br></li><li>Steam integrated with stats and achievements.</li></ul>",
